{"tid":2085792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可能係最後一晚10點鳩嗌，仲有冇人一齊嗌？七月一！維園見！","createTime":"2020-06-30T04:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T05:03:11.000Z","uid":108840,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"13d751c745cab0c59ce45f62d7f6b804f0e088a5","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"可能係最後一晚10點鳩嗌，仲有冇人一齊嗌？七月一！維園見！<br />\n<br />\n窗邊要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窗邊要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窗邊要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fb1d5940cd3068272f0f26daf0c23c22e8e3af","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d60f32a38b3b7612a6c96b3356b4223924008d70","tid":2085792,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ad7a195b71be245f34b16f709864714d760688","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"窗邊要人，最後機會"},{"pid":"2eef87c227b1c90922a44e5261240c8577cef38d","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:47:21.000Z","msg":"窗邊要人，最後機會"},{"pid":"71fadea831d2f7d29ba87121287e466ab09e434e","tid":2085792,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"7月1"},{"pid":"790e8872dcf1b6d4ebe60bcd9004ca7031c88329","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdba08801b78d8a4e97e5fea9a16a4afbf912319","tid":2085792,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CL9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=c1095e36\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"8721ca27029a8c76d0c3e683da2d02640f7bdaf5","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"七月一維園見"},{"pid":"559f60b2779480eb4e399d789aff5c3b5a2d0621","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:48:12.000Z","msg":"10點要人"},{"pid":"3a16c650902ac22476bf8007248c3477664974b1","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"一息尚存，抗爭到底"},{"pid":"ff6db279095118321f4945d5eb481ed896f522b1","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"7b74db2f669c6c058efd6a529691d468fab68c82","tid":2085792,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007af3644c1e3ce97acbaab8e0ab9c1b61a313cd","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"人呢？"},{"pid":"0f92cf00f158cec6274ff22c439f3c2292ef623e","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3742f0fd1a0758c44690804afc7a56fbf33661be","tid":2085792,"uid":168941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:50:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f963319477f6c1ad6400e97a6bd9d8a19aeda79","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"幾時先上到熱門？"},{"pid":"ad95abf6373fdda1c6e83a346670369c31d74203","tid":2085792,"uid":108840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"熱門見"},{"pid":"67ca97d7f32c498108346a78b8486e1f0e154ffc","tid":2085792,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,